<lb ed="I" n="0080a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>儁蒙文姬卅一人等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0080a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑側</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑側</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0080a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0080a0101"><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">夫</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">大</unclear>□□□薩云表<note n="0080001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30570"/>＝挺【史】</note><app n="0080001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">挺</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30570"/></rdg></app>世之容。妙法開敷。波若闡<note n="0080002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30562"/>＝權【史】</note><app n="0080002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30562"/></rdg></app>顯之音。如來
<lb ed="I" n="0080a02" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">奄</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">過</unclear>□□殊遷祀。像法<note n="0080003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30576"/>＝雖【史】</note><app n="0080003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30576"/></rdg></app>隆。床宗者尠。是以大代永熙二年
<lb ed="I" n="0080a03" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">歲</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">次</unclear>□□正月戊子朔八日乙未。北雍州宜君郡黃堡縣邑主儁蒙
<lb ed="I" n="0080a04" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">文</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">姬</unclear>□□娥合邑子卅一人等。自慨丕踰。流轉<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>竊。故減<note n="0080004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30428"/>＝割【史】</note><app n="0080004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">割</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30428"/></rdg></app>家珍。<note n="0080005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30571"/>＝聘【史】</note><app n="0080005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30571"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0080a05" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">名</unclear>□□□大路顯敞之處。敬造石像一區。功<note n="0080006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30455"/>＝就【史】</note><app n="0080006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">就</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30455"/></rdg></app><note n="0080007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30577"/>＝成【史】</note><app n="0080007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">成</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30577"/></rdg></app>訖。令<note n="0080008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30572"/>＝國【史】</note><app n="0080008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">國</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30572"/></rdg></app>祚永隆
<lb ed="I" n="0080a06" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">人</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">民</unclear>□　洽。下<note n="0080009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30573"/>＝願【史】</note><app n="0080009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30573"/></rdg></app>慶七世。永超八難。神<note n="0080010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30574"/>＝縣【史】</note><app n="0080010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">縣</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30574"/></rdg></app>福堂。濟生死之<note n="0080011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB25812"/>＝苦【史】</note><app n="0080011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB25812"/></rdg></app>。<app type="star" corresp="#0080009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30573"/></rdg></app>諸
<lb ed="I" n="0080a07" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">邑</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">子</unclear>□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">蒙</unclear>拯。眾患消□。□<app type="star" corresp="#0080009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30573"/></rdg></app><note n="0080012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30578"/>＝初【史】</note><app n="0080012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">初</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30578"/></rdg></app>首。書人夫蒙顯達。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
